  <brief_title>A Study to Determine the Effect of Montelukast Sodium as an Episode Modifier in the Treatment of Infrequent Episodic Asthma in Children (0476-165)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Study to Determine the Effect of Montelukast Sodium as an Episode Modifier in the Treatment of Infrequent Episodic Asthma in Children</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A 53-week study to determine the effect of montelukast sodium when given to children (with
      infrequent episodic asthma) at the earliest symptoms of an acute episode of asthma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
